dct_title_s: Mufassal Türkiye Cumhuriyei Haritası / Miralay Mehmet Neşet Bey.
dct_description_sm: Relief and depth shown by gradient tints. Prime meridian is Istanbul. This map was issued the year the modern Republic of Türkiye was founded. Shows major cities, state borders, roads, railroads, carriages/wagon roads.
